  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the melody from Johann Strauss, wonderful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have also one unique picture of this gypsy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I was in the war troupe, I was sitting and somebody-- later, I knew that this gay boy, Sigmund Kay, also.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He made this picture of-- of me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I was-- I had to-- I have to join this job morning by baker and evening in the other.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But with my nice job by baker, once they was finished-- because the beautiful lady, the woman of the baker-- she liked me not only as the delivery boy of bread, but even of her lovers' letters.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was 20 years younger than the husband, and I understood later that she expected something more, not from me because I was still a child.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she had many lovers in secretly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she used me as a letter boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it's happened that something once they [? rung, ?] I was fallen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was not the lover, but it was the wife of her lover-- of lover.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when I said her that once [? these ?] happened something wrong, probably she wanted that I will leave because she was afraid-- she afraid that it can be blackmailed or like this.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And rather for her marriage, it was very good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The-- the husband for her was very good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What she wanted, what she liked, she had everything because she was young.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She was very pretty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he did everything for her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, I had to leave my job in bakery against-- against wish of the baker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was wondering why before his wife appreciated so much that I will work there, and now she-- oh, better when-- when he leaves our job.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's better maybe.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
